.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pit Bulls Of Instagram on June 26, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Consider donating the money you would spend on fireworks to a rescue instead.'.

node.text:
@rebeccacorry
・・・
We can be patriotic without terrorizing dogs and all animals and the humans who have served our country. 

Please consider buying shelter supplies or making a donation to a charity instead of buying fireworks. 

#standupforpits 🇺🇸
